                            <comment id="479996" author="JIRAUSER19288" created="Tue, 2 Dec 2025 12:48:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hey &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=pjo&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;pjo&quot;&gt;pjo&lt;/a&gt;, this is another issue that will need further patches to complete. So far, this landed patch was some needed cleanup so that the nodemap import and export can be added later. I&apos;ll let you know once this is done&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="479923" author="pjo" created="Tue, 2 Dec 2025 04:10:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Merged for 2.17&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="479888" author="gerrit" created="Tue, 2 Dec 2025 03:42:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&quot;Oleg Drokin &amp;lt;green@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&quot; merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/58113/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/58113/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
